9	    /// always carries a resolved list, so it can't tell "user picked system" from "no choice yet").
10	    @AppStorage(AppLanguage.storageKey) private var languageSelection = AppLanguage.system.rawValue
11	    /// True once the picker is touched this session, so we surface the relaunch hint.
